# @testcase 14f
# @Receive message with a value in an incorrect data format (syntax) for a particular field identifier (tag number).

iCONNECT
# logon message and response
I8=FIX.4.135=A34=149=TW4152=<TIME>56=ISLD98=0108=2
E8=FIX.4.19=5835=A34=149=ISLD52=00000000-00:00:0056=TW4198=0108=210=0

